'' Thud ! What was that ? Efficiency had fainted dead away ! The last blow had been too much for her . 
And the Principles gathered mournfully round , but with the aid of the Propeller Slip and a friendly lift from the Surface she was at length revived and regained a more normal aspect . 
Such give back'' is known as slip , '' and anyone behind the propellor will feel the slip as a strong draught of air . 
'' Well , that sounds so common sense , '' sighed Efficiency , I suppose it must be true , and if the Designer is satisfied , that's all I really care about . 
